with the other side. That's the part that I think has been most missing, =
and is where using the AI as "other" could be really powerful. No?
>=20
> - Highlighting funny interactions sounds ideal, *especially where it =
makes people who are unwilling to engage or reconsider look foolish.* =
Again, if we make the focus of the program be about lauding Americans =
who are willing to engage and reconsider the "other side", and providing =
a narrative for average folks to do so themselves, then I think we have =
something that could run for multiple seasons.
>=20
