the conversation. No idea if this would work well or not, but if we =
could train an AI to review content sent to it (i.e., a "fake news =
filter") this could train people to spot fake news AND give us some =
great comedic content. Conversely, if a bot gave you a link and asked =
you if you thought it mattered to the conversation at hand that might be =
less confrontational than a human being saying "read the Wikipedia =
entry, asshole." Thoughts?
